  "texts": [
    "Additionally, AI can assist in crafting \"smart\" malware that learns from its environment, adjusts strategies to avoid detection, and maximizes the damage it inflicts.",
    "This renders traditional security defenses, such as signature-based malware detection, often inadequate against these advanced threats.",
    "One example of this emerging threat is DeepLocker, an AI-powered attack tool developed by IBM Research that conceals its malicious intent until it reaches a specific target, showcasing the potential future sophistication of malware threats.",
    "In essence, while AI undoubtedly enhances our defensive capabilities in cybersecurity, it also provides adversaries with tools to create more sophisticated, adaptable, and damaging attacks.",
    "The emerging reality of AI-powered cyber threats underscores the ongoing need to continuously evolve and improve our AI-based defenses while maintaining robust human oversight."
  ],
